vote.title: An ordinance granting a private license to Gaston & Good Latimer, LP, for the use of approximately 2 square feet of aerial space to occupy, maintain and utilize a premise blade sign over a portion of Elm Street right-of-way near its intersection with Good Latimer Expressway - Revenue: General Fund $1,000.00 annual fee, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
